    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A competitive and cooperative party game for 1–6 players!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each minigame lasts around 2–3 minutes, packed with fast-paced action you can enjoy in short bursts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports local multiplayer as well as Remote Play Together, so you can easily have fun with family and friends. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Free Mode]</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250820/extras/0ebf21054e39609803cf407f0d7388da.poster.avif?t=1771464191\" width=1170 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250820/extras/0ebf21054e39609803cf407f0d7388da.webm?t=1771464191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250820/extras/0ebf21054e39609803cf407f0d7388da.mp4?t=1771464191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the game you want to play! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Party Mode]</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250820/extras/16139a79351d813e8d58582c1e3a3f10.poster.avif?t=1771464191\" width=1170 height=524 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250820/extras/16139a79351d813e8d58582c1e3a3f10.webm?t=1771464191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250820/extras/16139a79351d813e8d58582c1e3a3f10.mp4?t=1771464191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play your chosen games in order </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and compete for the most points!</p>",
